Requires ocaml, csdp (no Debian package), ocaml-glpk (no Debian package)


To install Csdp:
* download it from https://projects.coin-or.org/Csdp/
  http://www.coin-or.org/download/source/Csdp/Csdp-6.1.1.tgz
* Apply our patchs (modified install target and enable the use of global
param.csdp)
  cd Csdp-6.1.1.tgz
  for i in path_to_osdp/external/csdp_*.patch; do patch -p0 < $i; done
* install dependencies:
  * libatlas-base-dev
  * libatlas-dev
  * libblas-dev
  * gfortran
* type make, sudo make install


To install OCaml-GLPK:
* download it from http://ocaml-glpk.sourceforge.net/
* install dependencies:
  * libglpk-dev from http://www.gnu.org/software/glpk/ (the version 4.35)
* type make opt, sudo make install


Autoconf :
% autoconf


Configure :
% ./configure
or
% ./configure --with-csdp-lib-path=PATH --with-csdp-inc-path=PATH --with-glpk-path=PATH

the default path is /usr/local/


To compile:
% make


To install (optional):
# make install
